# Blocklist Compiler - Ignore patterns

# ============================================
# Public source and review assets
# ============================================
# Keep scripts, config, workflows, constraints, README, public docs, tests,
# and small fixtures trackable. Generated blocklist data and diagnostics are
# ignored in the generated/runtime section below.

# ============================================
# ============================================
run.py
AGENTS.md

# ============================================
# Generated/runtime outputs
# ============================================
lists/
.cache/
reports/
state.json

